trans-unit.source: Contains response information returned as a result of a peer endpoint resolution operation on the peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: 包含對等解析程式上的對等端點解析作業結果傳回的回應資訊。

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.CustomPeerResolverService.Resolve%28System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo%29> or an implementation of <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.IPeerResolverContract.Resolve%28System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo%29> is called, this object is returned to the client.
trans-unit.target: 當<xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.CustomPeerResolverService.Resolve%28System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo%29>或實作<xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.IPeerResolverContract.Resolve%28System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo%29>是呼叫，這個物件會傳回至用戶端。</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.IPeerResolverContract.Resolve%28System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo%29> </xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.CustomPeerResolverService.Resolve%28System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo%29>

trans-unit.source: It contains the endpoints registered to the peer specified in a previous corresponding <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo> instance sent to the peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: 它包含註冊的對等的前一個對應中指定的端點<xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo>傳送至對等解析程式執行個體。</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveInfo>

trans-unit.source: Instances of this class are primarily used to pass information from the resolver service to a network client of that service.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別的執行個體主要用於從解析程式服務傳遞資訊至該服務的網路用戶端。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new default instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveResponseInfo"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化新的預設執行個體的<xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveResponseInfo"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveResponseInfo"></xref> class with the provided set of peer endpoint addresses.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.ResolveResponseInfo"></xref>類別提供一組對等端點位址。

trans-unit.source: Array of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerNodeAddress"></xref> objects that contain the endpoint addresses registered to the peer whose endpoints were requested in a previous resolution operation.
trans-unit.target: 陣列<xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerNodeAddress"></xref>物件，其中包含端點位址註冊的對等的前一個解析作業中被要求提供其端點。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a collection of peer node addresses.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定對等節點位址的集合。

trans-unit.source: Generic list <IList> of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerNodeAddress"></xref> objects that contain the endpoint addresses registered to the peer whose endpoints were requested in a previous resolution operation.
trans-unit.target: 泛型清單<IList>的<xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerNodeAddress"></xref>物件，其中包含端點位址註冊的對等的前一個解析作業中被要求提供其端點。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the body of the message containing a serialized instance of this type is correctly formed.
trans-unit.target: 指出是否包含這個型別的序列化執行個體的訊息本文格式是否正確。

trans-unit.source: True if the resolution response information body is correctly-formed by the sender; false if it is not.
trans-unit.target: 如果解析回應資訊主體已由傳送者; 正確格式，則為 true。如果不是，false。
